playing here at Google

00:03:24.660 --> 00:03:29.490
is, in my mind, the ultimate
statement about inclusion,

00:03:29.490 --> 00:03:32.700
about integration,
and that, I believe,

00:03:32.700 --> 00:03:35.100
is the measure of any program--

00:03:35.100 --> 00:03:38.040
whether or not we can
get them into a situation

00:03:38.040 --> 00:03:42.310
where they can fulfill their
dreams in such a manner.

